Welcome to the MSSTI Github repository for my MODs for phpBB3.

******************************************************************************
* Title :
* BB3 Media Player Version 0.0.8
******************************************************************************
* Description:
* Adds a JW FLV player in the Media Player page that captures all supported media (by default flv, mp3)
* stored on phpbb_root/mplayer/media including sub folders and display it 
* as one playlist playable in the Media player page
******************************************************************************
* Please keep in mind that this is still early in development, so not everything is in place or working.
* It is not recommended that you install it on a live forum.
* Let me know if you find anything broken, though, so I can take a look.
* Also, good ideas and bug reports are always welcome.
******************************************************************************
* phpBB version: phpbb 3.0.7-PL1
******************************************************************************
* Requirements: JavaScript enabled
******************************************************************************
* License: GNU General Public License v2
******************************************************************************
* Before adding this MOD to your forum, you should back up all files related to this MOD.]
******************************************************************************
